functions.name: validate_token
functions.signature: pub fn validate_token(token: &str, secret: &str) -> Result<Claims, TokenError>
functions.description: Validates a JWT token and returns the claims

functions.name: generate_token
functions.signature: pub fn generate_token(user_id: &str, role: Role, config: &TokenConfig) -> Result<String, TokenError>

types.name: Claims
types.definition: pub struct Claims { user_id: String, role: Role, exp: u64, iat: u64 }

types.name: Role
types.definition: pub enum Role { Admin, User, Guest }

types.name: TokenConfig
types.definition: pub struct TokenConfig { secret: String, expires_in_secs: u64 }
